<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٤٩٧ - المسيب بن واضح السلمي، الحِمْصِيّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">• قال الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ:</span> ضعيف. <span class="c2">«السنن»</span> ١ ٧٥ و٨٠ و٤ ٢٨٠.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">• وقال السُّلَمِيُّ:</span> سألت الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ عنه،<span class="c5"> فقال:</span> ضعيف. <span class="c2">«الميزان»</span> ٤ <span class="c2">(٨٥٤٨)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>